[
    {
        "text": "By 2040, they estimate 40% of households will be single people.",
        "startTime": 401,
        "endTime": 4659,
        "slowStartTime": 751,
        "slowEndTime": 7213
    },
    {
        "text": "So, the traditional family is already departed.",
        "startTime": 5401,
        "endTime": 10155,
        "slowStartTime": 8252,
        "slowEndTime": 15457
    },
    {
        "text": "State policies are racing to catch up with realities on the ground.",
        "startTime": 10459,
        "endTime": 16438,
        "slowStartTime": 15838,
        "slowEndTime": 24882
    },
    {
        "text": "That day can't come fast enough for Masami Onishi.",
        "startTime": 16920,
        "endTime": 20429,
        "slowStartTime": 25530,
        "slowEndTime": 30868
    },
    {
        "text": "At home, the 24-year-old single mother handles her two young daughters with ease...",
        "startTime": 20582,
        "endTime": 25611,
        "slowStartTime": 31023,
        "slowEndTime": 38641
    },
    {
        "text": "...but she says, it hasn't always been the case.",
        "startTime": 25719,
        "endTime": 28629,
        "slowStartTime": 38729,
        "slowEndTime": 43168
    },
    {
        "text": "The single mother works 6 hours a day, 6 days a week just to earn 800 US dollars a month.",
        "startTime": 29515,
        "endTime": 35752,
        "slowStartTime": 44422,
        "slowEndTime": 53853
    },
    {
        "text": "The government wants to put more single mothers to work...",
        "startTime": 36343,
        "endTime": 39546,
        "slowStartTime": 54664,
        "slowEndTime": 59544
    },
    {
        "text": "...in order to reduce the 50% poverty rate among them.",
        "startTime": 39637,
        "endTime": 43390,
        "slowStartTime": 59605,
        "slowEndTime": 65310
    },
    {
        "text": "But, as Ms. Onishi's case shows, it doesn't really help.",
        "startTime": 43745,
        "endTime": 47668,
        "slowStartTime": 65768,
        "slowEndTime": 71727
    },
    {
        "text": "Poverty rate of single mothers doesn't change very much...",
        "startTime": 48473,
        "endTime": 52601,
        "slowStartTime": 72859,
        "slowEndTime": 79127
    },
    {
        "text": "...even if the mother is working.",
        "startTime": 52698,
        "endTime": 55127,
        "slowStartTime": 79197,
        "slowEndTime": 82915
    },
    {
        "text": "Because they have very weak position in the labor market...",
        "startTime": 55485,
        "endTime": 60259,
        "slowStartTime": 83377,
        "slowEndTime": 90614
    },
    {
        "text": "...because of the very huge gender gap, wage gap, in Japan.",
        "startTime": 60387,
        "endTime": 65811,
        "slowStartTime": 90730,
        "slowEndTime": 98941
    },
    {
        "text": "Doctor Zhou said it's crucial...",
        "startTime": 66567,
        "endTime": 68192,
        "slowStartTime": 100001,
        "slowEndTime": 102513
    },
    {
        "text": "...that the government boosts welfare support to single mothers...",
        "startTime": 68260,
        "endTime": 71743,
        "slowStartTime": 102540,
        "slowEndTime": 107839
    },
    {
        "text": "...because children raised in poverty aren't likely to escape even when they grow up.",
        "startTime": 71821,
        "endTime": 77249,
        "slowStartTime": 107882,
        "slowEndTime": 116098
    },
    {
        "text": "Yasuko Kawabe who started the dining hall for children of single mothers...",
        "startTime": 77607,
        "endTime": 81757,
        "slowStartTime": 116561,
        "slowEndTime": 122860
    },
    {
        "text": "...says that's precisely what she's seen over the years...",
        "startTime": 81852,
        "endTime": 85299,
        "slowStartTime": 122928,
        "slowEndTime": 128173
    },
    {
        "text": "...and she hopes an alternative route could open up soon.",
        "startTime": 85615,
        "endTime": 89076,
        "slowStartTime": 128572,
        "slowEndTime": 133839
    },
    {
        "text": "In an ageing society that desperately needs more future taxpayers,...",
        "startTime": 90097,
        "endTime": 94977,
        "slowStartTime": 135295,
        "slowEndTime": 142691
    },
    {
        "text": "...the government needs to help children of single parents...",
        "startTime": 95068,
        "endTime": 98369,
        "slowStartTime": 142752,
        "slowEndTime": 147779
    },
    {
        "text": "...become contributing members to society...",
        "startTime": 98455,
        "endTime": 101226,
        "slowStartTime": 147833,
        "slowEndTime": 152064
    },
    {
        "text": "...rather than seeing them as a burden and a disgrace.",
        "startTime": 101461,
        "endTime": 105185,
        "slowStartTime": 152342,
        "slowEndTime": 158002
    }
]